response.overview: S.M.A.C.K.: 50 Cent and Kanye West, Vol. 13 movie was released Nov 06, 2007 by the EMI Music Canada studio. This street music & arts DVD magazine features segments with 50 Cent, Nelly & Bow Wow, DJ Toomp, Kanye West, Lil Wayne, Young Jeezy, Ja Rule, Shea Davis, Boyz N Da Hood, Joel Ortiz, Gucci Mane, Young Buck, Nore, Styles P, Mazardi Fox, and Red Cafe.
